    Scope and Contents
The Instructional Services Librarians Subject file, 1970-86 consists of memoranda, reports, correspondence, minutes, planning materials pertaining to the library and the librarians of SSU.  The file also contains safety and security procedures, relations with SSU faculty and visitors, policies concerning Gift books, book prices and library objectives and personnel policies.  
  
